description:
"I hope you enjoy the video!" -Me(Tamers12345)
"Don't worry Tamers, they definitely will!" -Sonic
"Hm hm hm. My bitch is right Tamers. The video is quite amazing." -Bartleby
"Don't forget to subscribe!" -Manic
"Don't forget to comment too bitches!" -Knuckles
"You can also like the video if you want too!" -Sonia
"If you comment, I may just give you a kiss." -Mindy
"Also be sure to tell Tamers12345 what his next video should be!" - Queen Aleena
"That's right! It's thanks to you guys, his fans, that he makes these videos in the first place!" -Uncle Chuck
"Yeah." -Mindy's dad

"Well, I guess you guys already said what needs to be said. :D lol" -Me(Tamers1234)
fulltitle: Tamers12345 & Co. Would Like To Wish You A Merry Christmas

comments.text: tamers, would you ever consider making a sonic underground movie? like a full video maybe an hour long. i would really like to see it especially if there is a lot of bardonic moments in it!
comments.author: LYRA!

replies.text: +kokuhaku akaboji I might. If I did, it would probably take a while. Most of my animations take a couple weeks to make since I (believe it or not) draw everything frame by frame.
replies.author: Tamers12345

comments.text: can you please do a Sonic Underground: Where are they Now?
comments.author: kompacktdisk

replies.text: +VoxelPie I was actually thinking of doing that sometime, i even drew out character designs and everything. But the more i think about it,  im not to sure. Part of the beauty of Sonic Underground is that it's ending is left as a complete mystery. Its like a poem, and not every poem needs an ending  <:)
replies.author: Tamers12345
